### Ver plan de estudio del alumno autenticado (reemplazar {alumnoId})
GET http://localhost/api/alumnos/{$alumnoId}/plan-estudio
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar estado de una materia del alumno
PATCH http://localhost/api/alumnos/{$alumnoId}/materias/{$materiaId}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "estado": "regularizada",
  "nota": 8,
  "fecha_estado": "2025-01-15 00:00:00"
}

### Ver plan base de una carrera (admin)
GET http://localhost/api/carreras/{$carreraId}/plan
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

